    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >试玩版特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1名主角</strong>（魔王）和<strong>1名辅助角色</strong>（妻子）。完整版将包含<strong>4名主角</strong>和<strong>4名辅助角色</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>仅包含第一世界</strong>。完整版将开放<strong>第二世界</strong>及<strong>隐藏关卡/最终Boss</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>默认难度</strong>。完整版将加入<strong>多个进阶难度</strong>，包含更多机制和敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>试玩限定的额外关卡</strong>：尽可能对<strong>RnGesus</strong>造成伤害，并根据<strong>总伤害量</strong>获得高分！这既是<strong>高分挑战模式</strong>，提升可玩性，也是衡量<strong>你的卡组强度</strong>的测试场！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《RnGesus Slayer》：它是《杀戮尖塔》遇上老虎机！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《RnGesus Slayer》</strong>是一款Roguelike卡组构筑游戏，你拥有<strong>3个独立卡组</strong>，并通过<strong>转动老虎机</strong>抽取卡牌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031290/extras/272c8d375497400a0ab0c72b6e290b9d.poster.avif?t=1747171919\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031290/extras/272c8d375497400a0ab0c72b6e290b9d.webm?t=1747171919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031290/extras/272c8d375497400a0ab0c72b6e290b9d.mp4?t=1747171919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >相同类型的卡牌落在一起时会<strong>触发连击</strong>，生成<strong>升级版卡牌</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031290/extras/49ac403efbe22974cc6cf903391203e8.poster.avif?t=1747171919\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031290/extras/49ac403efbe22974cc6cf903391203e8.webm?t=1747171919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031290/extras/49ac403efbe22974cc6cf903391203e8.mp4?t=1747171919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用<strong>武器卡</strong>攻击女神的仆从，使用<strong>魔法卡</strong>获取法力施放技能，并使用<strong>金币卡</strong>升级卡组！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031290/extras/d84fb2dd5ad836b67fdc97d1106504bf.poster.avif?t=1747171919\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031290/extras/d84fb2dd5ad836b67fdc97d1106504bf.webm?t=1747171919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031290/extras/d84fb2dd5ad836b67fdc97d1106504bf.mp4?t=1747171919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的<strong>独特法术</strong>，助你消灭敌人、强化手牌/卡组，或操控老虎机为你所用！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031290/extras/155be617f8177b06725cbbde87c2d907.poster.avif?t=1747171919\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031290/extras/155be617f8177b06725cbbde87c2d907.webm?t=1747171919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031290/extras/155be617f8177b06725cbbde87c2d907.mp4?t=1747171919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特的法术与能力系统，包含35+法术、15+强化效果，以及45+敌人等你挑战！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autopl